data.description:
Back to the market at no fault of the seller. Buyer couldn't perform, contingency buyer selling their home. Great Investment Property or home for a handy-homeowner who wants equity!
With a little TLC, this can be your dream home! Some cosmetics updates could turn this house from "drab" to "FAB".
 Beautiful custom-built open plan. Large Gourmet Kitchen with unique features: Island, Breakfast bar, Pull out shelves & spice rack, 2 lazy susans, cookie sheet cab, 2 pantries, all appliances stay including French Door Stainless Steel refrigerator & has floor vacuum—spacious finished basement with a fabulous wet bar. Bar fridge stays. Family room, or recreational room, Security System. Stamped concrete & much more. Large backyard perfect for summer barbeques and entertaining family and friends. This gorgeous house comes with the following unique features, Smart house 2 Kevo deadbolts, Phillips Hue bulbs outside, Ring video doorbell, Ring spotlight camera, Ring floodlight camera  Alexa Show 15, WeMo Smart switches, 3 Wi-Fi ceiling fans, Nest thermostat, 2 Ring Cameras. The garage comes with a Workshop and a Rubbermaid FastTrack garage organizer system. The property is occupied—The property is sold as is.
